<figureCitation id="25C375B011268D8E0BCF64C7520894BC" captionStart="Figure 124" captionStartId="F124" captionText="Figure 124. Ipomoea spruceana. A habit B outer sepal C middle sepal D inner sepal E corolla opened out to show stamens F ovary and style G fruiting inflorescence. Drawn by Rosemary Wise from Spruce 703." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/391126" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">124</figureCitation>
